without you, do you?

00:30:13.937 --> 00:30:16.981
If I become someone
indispensable in your life

00:30:18.441 --> 00:30:19.609
I'd be honored.

00:30:23.321 --> 00:30:26.533
Anyway, will you be able
to shoot tomorrow?

00:30:27.992 --> 00:30:29.035
I'm worried.

00:30:29.661 --> 00:30:31.538
Maybe I should get you
some herbal medicine.

00:30:34.999 --> 00:30:37.877
