00:30:42.048 --> 00:30:43.049
Good.

00:30:44.592 --> 00:30:48.513
But I'm still worried,
so I'll stop by the set tomorrow.

00:30:49.347 --> 00:30:51.057
And I'll drive you home afterward.

00:30:51.599 --> 00:30:52.809
Is that okay?

00:31:29.846 --> 00:31:30.889
Long time no see.

00:31:32.181 --> 00:31:35.351
- You doing all right?
- How is Ah-jin?

00:31:35.685 --> 00:31:36.853
You're unbelievable.

00:31:37.353 --> 00:31:39.522
If you were so worried,
why are you showing up now?

00:31:41.316 --> 00:31:42.525
She's in danger.

00:31:42.609 --> 00:31:44.777
What do you mean, she's in danger?

00:31:44.861 --> 00:31:46.154
It's her husband.

00:31:47.030 --> 00:31:49.324
Do-hyuk, that bastard,
is completely insane.

00:31:49.407 --> 00:31:50.909
He's shady in more ways than one.

00:31:51.367 --> 00:31:53.202
I think Ah-jin fell into his trap.

00:31:53.786 --> 00:31:56.706
Do you have proof
for what you just said?

00:31:56.789 --> 00:31:57.916
That's the problem.

00:31:57.999 --> 00:32:00.752
I don't have any evidence
to prove that he's nuts.

00:32:01.586 --> 00:32:04.881
Ah-jin called me not long ago,
saying something felt off about him.

00:32:05.381 --> 00:32:07.634
But she doesn't even remember
making that call.

00:32:07.717 --> 00:32:10.303
That's why you and I
need to help her.

00:32:10.386 --> 00:32:11.888
Do you get what I'm saying?

00:32:13.348 --> 00:32:14.766
I'm not sure.

00:32:16.142 --> 00:32:18.394
It feels like we'd be interfering
with her life.

00:32:18.478 --> 00:32:20.730
What part of what I just said
did you not understand?

00:32:20.813 --> 00:32:21.856
Her husband--

00:32:21.940 --> 00:32:24.025
You just said you had no proof.

00:32:24.108 --> 00:32:27.028
