He went to work out.

00:40:48.988 --> 00:40:50.614
You got here earlier than I expected.

00:40:55.536 --> 00:40:57.580
Why did you have the script changed?

00:40:57.663 --> 00:40:58.664
Right.

00:40:59.665 --> 00:41:01.000
I already told you.

00:41:01.459 --> 00:41:04.753
I want you to rely on me completely

00:41:04.837 --> 00:41:07.047
but you clearly have
no intention of doing that.

00:41:11.510 --> 00:41:12.553
Turns out

00:41:13.471 --> 00:41:14.972
I have to push you this hard

00:41:15.931 --> 00:41:18.476
for you to come running to me.

00:41:19.602 --> 00:41:20.603
Figures.

00:41:21.395 --> 00:41:24.607
I guess leaking those cheap
tabloid articles wasn't enough.

00:41:25.900 --> 00:41:28.068
So those articles were your doing.

00:41:29.195 --> 00:41:30.571
Why are you doing this to me?

00:41:34.074 --> 00:41:37.536
I gave you everything you wanted,
didn't I?

00:41:40.247 --> 00:41:42.791
The least you can do
is make me happy in return.

00:41:44.376 --> 00:41:46.086
I've always done my best for you.

00:41:47.379 --> 00:41:48.589
This is really hurtful.

00:41:54.803 --> 00:41:56.931
Take those articles down now.

00:41:58.307 --> 00:41:59.558
If I take them down

00:42:00.643 --> 00:42:04.438
does that mean you'll behave
the way I want you to?

00:42:04.897 --> 00:42:07.399
Why should I live my life
the way you want?

00:42:08.275 --> 00:42:10.694
Because I like you.

00:42:16.867 --> 00:42:20.246
Unfortunately,
my ex-wife broke too easily

00:42:21.413 --> 00:42:23.040
for all the effort I put into her.

00:42:23.499 --> 00:42:26.669
But I feel like
you will stay by my side

00:42:27.127 --> 00:42:29.255
with that pretty face of yours.

00:42:30.464 --> 00:42:34.760
You'll keep me entertained,
just like you always have.

00:42:35.135 --> 00:42:37.888
That's why I took you in
when you were so pitiful.

00:42:41.183 --> 00:42:42.476
Fuck you.

00:42:49.692 --> 00:42:50.901
You son of a bitch.

00:42:56.657 --> 00:42:57.700
If you feel wronged...

00:43:00.369 --> 00:43:01.996
Right. Think of it as punishment.

00:43:02.329 --> 00:43:03.539
"Punishment"?

00:43:03.831 --> 00:43:05.207
You said it yourself.

00:43:06.208 --> 00:43:08.586
I thought I was being punished.

00:43:09.545 --> 00:43:11.630
Why do you think
you're being punished?

00:43:14.008 --> 00:43:17.678
When my mom begged me to save her

00:43:17.761 --> 00:43:20.055
I just stood there and watched.

00:43:20.139 --> 00:43:23.142
I thought all of this
was punishment for that.

00:43:29.273 --> 00:43:30.441
You don't remember?

00:43:31.442 --> 00:43:33.152
Is this a dream?

00:43:33.569 --> 00:43:35.613
You didn't come to me before.

00:43:36.822 --> 00:43:38.782
You acted as if
you'd never see me again.

00:43:40.117 --> 00:43:41.744
Of course, this is a dream.

00:43:43.037 --> 00:43:44.204
When you wake up

00:43:45.414 --> 00:43:46.957
you won't remember any of this.

00:43:50.044 --> 00:43:51.045
So?

00:43:53.505 --> 00:43:54.923
Is it starting to come back to you?

00:43:57.801 --> 00:44:01.263
Ah-jin,
I have plenty of ways to corner you.

00:44:01.347 --> 00:44:03.974
Your past could be exposed
at any time.

00:44:04.058 --> 00:44:06.727
And when that happens,
that fall is going to hurt.

00:44:11.607 --> 00:44:13.776
That's the end of my patience.

00:44:14.068 --> 00:44:17.488
If you don't want to lose
everything I've given you...

00:44:18.614 --> 00:44:20.532
If you want to stay
right where you are

00:44:22.201 --> 00:44:26.121
then I'm sure you know
exactly what you have to do.

00:44:33.629 --> 00:44:34.797
Ah-jin.

00:44:36.507 --> 00:44:37.675
You're a smart girl.

00:45:21.009 --> 00:45:22.219
Shit.

00:45:28.600 --> 00:45:29.935
This is Moon Do-hyuk.

00:45:30.018 --> 00:45:31.478
You know who I am, right?

00:45:31.895 --> 00:45:34.606
What is this about?
How did you get my number--

00:45:34.690 --> 00:45:37.025
My wife isn't doing so well right now

00:45:37.109 --> 00:45:39.653
so I'd like you
to look after her for me.

00:45:42.114 --> 00:45:43.949
I'm a little tired after my workout

00:45:44.658 --> 00:45:46.577
so I'm thinking of sleeping
at a hotel tonight.

00:45:46.869 --> 00:45:48.495
Where is Ah-jin right now?

00:45:48.954 --> 00:45:51.081
Just come to the address
I'm sending you.

00:46:09.558 --> 00:46:10.559
Ah-jin.

00:46:12.019 --> 00:46:13.020
You...

00:46:26.867 --> 00:46:29.077
Let's get you out of here.
You'll catch a cold.

00:46:36.794 --> 00:46:38.378
Jun-seo.

00:46:42.257 --> 00:46:44.343
Do you know what I realized today?

00:46:49.264 --> 00:46:50.349
I realized...

00:46:52.643 --> 00:46:54.937
I could still be thrown away.

00:47:02.277 --> 00:47:03.445
After all I've done...

00:47:05.656 --> 00:47:07.783
After all I've done to climb up here

00:47:09.368 --> 00:47:13.497
how can I still be someone
who gets thrown away?

00:47:15.040 --> 00:47:16.333
How is that even possible?

00:47:18.085 --> 00:47:21.046
Ah-jin, you need to calm down.

00:47:23.090 --> 00:47:25.050
This is so humiliating!

00:47:37.980 --> 00:47:39.189
I'm going to take it.

00:47:39.898 --> 00:47:41.817
I'm going to take Do-hyuk's position.

00:47:42.526 --> 00:47:46.363
I'm going to get rid of him
and take his place.

00:47:48.115 --> 00:47:49.199
I can do it.

00:47:49.283 --> 00:47:50.325
Right?

00:47:51.243 --> 00:47:54.830
Jun-seo, help me. Please?

00:47:54.913 --> 00:47:57.875
This is the man who had his ex-wife
locked up in a mental hospital.

00:47:57.958 --> 00:48:00.669
He tracked down my number
and called me to come get you.

00:48:01.086 --> 00:48:03.422
You know exactly how dangerous he is.

00:48:03.839 --> 00:48:04.840
So what?

00:48:06.049 --> 00:48:08.594
- What about it?
- You're the one who will break!

00:48:09.052 --> 00:48:11.471
You're going to break before he does.

00:48:11.555 --> 00:48:13.807
Why don't you see
how dangerous he really is?

00:48:13.891 --> 00:48:15.100
It's not fair.

00:48:16.518 --> 00:48:19.938
Why is he allowed to do
whatever he wants, and I'm not?

00:48:20.898 --> 00:48:23.066
Why am I always the one
who has to suffer?

00:48:23.609 --> 00:48:28.196
Why am I the only one
who has to fear hitting rock bottom?

00:48:28.822 --> 00:48:31.742
Why?

00:48:33.118 --> 00:48:36.038
Why?

00:48:39.458 --> 00:48:40.959
I can do it.

00:48:43.795 --> 00:48:44.880
I've got this.

00:48:45.547 --> 00:48:46.548
Right?

00:48:49.343 --> 00:48:50.385
I will...

00:48:51.720 --> 00:48:53.055
I'll get rid of that jerk.

00:49:30.342 --> 00:49:32.427
Why did I...

00:49:51.488 --> 00:49:54.992
Ah-jin, what's going on?
Are you okay?

00:49:55.409 --> 00:49:56.535
Where are you?

00:49:56.618 --> 00:49:57.953
Jae-oh.

00:49:59.913 --> 00:50:01.748
I can't hold on anymore.

00:50:05.210 --> 00:50:06.211
Ah-jin.

00:50:07.045 --> 00:50:09.047
Don't worry.
I'm going to fix everything.

00:50:10.549 --> 00:50:11.717
I'm ready.

00:50:19.975 --> 00:50:21.059
Jae-oh.

00:50:23.687 --> 00:50:26.314
Why do you do all this for me?

00:50:31.903 --> 00:50:34.156
You don't expect anything from me.

00:50:38.493 --> 00:50:41.705
And you do whatever I ask you to.

00:50:46.543 --> 00:50:48.003
It feels strange.

00:50:51.173 --> 00:50:52.591
I don't understand it.

00:50:58.930 --> 00:51:00.640
I just like being by your side.

00:51:02.684 --> 00:51:05.020
Maybe it's because
I don't have much in my life

00:51:06.563 --> 00:51:08.106
but you're everything to me.

00:51:12.944 --> 00:51:15.238
Every time I help you
get what you want...

00:51:16.615 --> 00:51:19.159
Every time I make things
easier for you...

00:51:21.453 --> 00:51:23.830
you have no idea how useful I feel.

00:51:29.086 --> 00:51:30.253
So go ahead, Ah-jin.

00:51:31.755 --> 00:51:33.131
Use me all you want.

00:51:34.424 --> 00:51:35.801
That's what I want.

00:52:02.911 --> 00:52:06.164
You've finished your IV drip.
Let me take it out for you.

00:52:09.501 --> 00:52:10.877
All done, ma'am.

00:52:34.860 --> 00:52:37.237
You seem to be doing better today.
That's a relief.

00:52:38.363 --> 00:52:39.447
Do I?

00:52:41.324 --> 00:52:42.701
Why is that a relief, though?

00:52:43.285 --> 00:52:46.371
After what happened
during the last shoot...

00:52:46.454 --> 00:52:47.455
What happened?

00:52:48.331 --> 00:52:49.916
I don't really remember.

00:52:50.500 --> 00:52:53.211
It's best not to dwell
on the unpleasant things.

00:52:53.920 --> 00:52:56.882
Forget what happened,
and good luck on your last shoot.

00:53:03.513 --> 00:53:04.598
Hi, Do-hyuk.

00:53:19.070 --> 00:53:20.322
Is today your last shoot?

00:53:20.739 --> 00:53:21.740
Yes.

00:53:22.324 --> 00:53:25.702
I'm going on a business trip tonight,
so I won't have time later.

00:53:26.620 --> 00:53:27.954
But I wanted to congratulate you.

00:53:29.998 --> 00:53:30.999
Thanks.

00:53:40.425 --> 00:53:41.635
Do you feel all right now?

00:53:42.510 --> 00:53:43.511
What do you mean?

00:53:44.137 --> 00:53:45.931
You were mad at me last night.

00:53:46.973 --> 00:53:48.350
I kept thinking about it.

00:53:48.433 --> 00:53:50.810
When we were at the swimming pool,
you called me

00:53:51.561 --> 00:53:53.271
a son of a bitch.

00:53:55.106 --> 00:53:56.274
It was pretty intense.

00:53:59.736 --> 00:54:00.820
What's wrong?

00:54:00.904 --> 00:54:02.697
You must have dreamed that.

00:54:03.531 --> 00:54:05.784
When did I go
to the swimming pool with you?

00:54:10.789 --> 00:54:11.873
You don't remember?

00:54:17.212 --> 00:54:20.548
Do-hyuk, are you teasing me?

00:54:21.716 --> 00:54:24.344
I would never say something
that awful to you.

00:54:24.761 --> 00:54:27.764
You were the one who held my hand
when I was struggling the most.

00:55:11.308 --> 00:55:12.309
Get out.

00:55:12.809 --> 00:55:14.227
Get out of the car, asshole!

00:55:19.607 --> 00:55:21.609
You didn't get hurt
as badly as I'd hoped.

00:55:22.277 --> 00:55:23.278
What a shame.

00:55:23.653 --> 00:55:25.322
What the hell? Who are you?

00:55:27.657 --> 00:55:29.617
You know me, right? Kim Jae-oh.

00:55:29.701 --> 00:55:32.662
I'm the guy you tried to burn alive
when you set my office on fire.

00:55:35.707 --> 00:55:37.459
I almost died that day.

00:55:38.418 --> 00:55:40.754
So I'm here to return the favor.

00:55:46.301 --> 00:55:48.470
I don't know
what you're talking about

00:55:49.220 --> 00:55:51.639
but if you value your life,
you'd better drop that idea.

00:55:52.057 --> 00:55:53.099
No, thanks.

00:55:53.767 --> 00:55:55.352
I know everything now.

00:55:56.936 --> 00:55:59.439
You're the one with the cross tattoo.

00:55:59.522 --> 00:56:00.940
Who was the other one?

00:56:02.275 --> 00:56:03.276
Moon Do-hyuk.

00:56:03.943 --> 00:56:05.528
The obnoxious psycho.

00:56:08.490 --> 00:56:10.325
I'll make both your lives
a living hell

00:56:11.201 --> 00:56:12.243
until the day I die.

00:56:13.953 --> 00:56:14.954
How does that sound?

00:56:15.705 --> 00:56:16.873
Fun, right?

00:56:26.716 --> 00:56:27.759
See you around.

00:56:52.242 --> 00:56:53.410
Yes, go ahead.

00:56:53.493 --> 00:56:55.078
Sir, we have a problem.

00:56:55.453 --> 00:56:56.496
What problem?

00:56:56.579 --> 00:56:58.039
Kim Jae-oh came to see me.

00:56:58.748 --> 00:57:01.876
He said he knew everything
about the fire and threatened me.

00:57:01.960 --> 00:57:04.629
He even warned me
that he would repay the favor.

00:57:05.547 --> 00:57:06.548
So?

00:57:06.631 --> 00:57:09.217
It looks like
he'll come after you too.

00:57:10.385 --> 00:57:12.846
Should we eliminate him for good?

00:57:13.805 --> 00:57:17.642
Some people don't know their place,
even when we treat them gently.

00:57:18.059 --> 00:57:20.645
They never appreciate
how lenient we are.

00:57:20.728 --> 00:57:23.857
Take care of Kim Jae-oh
however you want.

00:57:25.900 --> 00:57:27.944
Just make sure
I never hear about him again.

00:57:28.236 --> 00:57:29.529
I don't want his name

00:57:30.572 --> 00:57:33.950
ruining another meal with my wife.

00:57:35.869 --> 00:57:36.995
Get to it, then.

00:57:54.804 --> 00:57:56.055
Wait, hold on.

00:57:57.640 --> 00:57:59.726
- Come on.
- Seriously.

00:57:59.809 --> 00:58:01.394
Why do you look so ugly today?

00:58:01.478 --> 00:58:02.812
Which lane? I'm going jungle.

00:58:02.896 --> 00:58:04.564
- I'm going jungle.
- Me too.

00:58:04.647 --> 00:58:06.024
The worst player buys ramyeon.

00:58:08.109 --> 00:58:09.486
- All right.
- Sounds good.

00:58:09.569 --> 00:58:10.820
I'm right below Seung-jae.

00:58:10.904 --> 00:58:13.114
- I'm safe.
- Isn't Yun-ho the worst, though?

00:58:13.198 --> 00:58:15.617
- What are you talking about?
- He's the worst.

00:58:15.700 --> 00:58:16.784
That's right, kid.

00:58:17.494 --> 00:58:19.329
Just keep living like you are now.

00:58:20.288 --> 00:58:23.291
Eat well, hang out with your friends

00:58:24.042 --> 00:58:27.462
get your diploma
and get into a good college.

00:58:28.713 --> 00:58:30.924
- He's the worst jungler.
- Come on.

00:58:35.094 --> 00:58:36.888
You don't need me anymore.

00:58:37.514 --> 00:58:39.432
No, he's better.

00:58:53.863 --> 00:58:54.864
Hey.

00:58:54.948 --> 00:58:56.950
We're all set over here.

00:58:57.033 --> 00:58:58.535
Okay, thank you.

00:58:58.826 --> 00:58:59.953
By the way

00:59:00.036 --> 00:59:02.705
you set everything up
exactly the way I asked, right?

00:59:02.789 --> 00:59:04.499
I told you not to worry.

00:59:05.041 --> 00:59:07.627
Why are you always so suspicious?

00:59:07.710 --> 00:59:08.836
Don't you trust me?

00:59:10.213 --> 00:59:11.422
It's not that.

00:59:11.923 --> 00:59:13.508
It's just that
this is really important.

00:59:14.384 --> 00:59:15.385
Anyway...

00:59:16.636 --> 00:59:17.720
Thank you.

00:59:55.216 --> 00:59:56.217
Damn it.

00:59:56.968 --> 00:59:57.969
Get him!

00:59:59.095 --> 01:00:00.597
- Get him!
- Get him!

01:00:00.680 --> 01:00:01.681
Stop him!

01:00:01.764 --> 01:00:04.017
- Get him!
- Catch him!

01:00:04.100 --> 01:00:06.019
Ready, action.

01:00:12.609 --> 01:00:13.693
Open the door.

01:00:14.569 --> 01:00:16.696
Why is it always so loud in there?

01:00:17.989 --> 01:00:20.950
I'm settling this today

01:00:21.034 --> 01:00:23.244
so stop acting like you're not home
and open up.

01:00:24.954 --> 01:00:26.331
I knew it.

01:00:27.415 --> 01:00:29.667
I knew you were home.

01:00:30.501 --> 01:00:31.753
Why aren't you answering...

01:00:33.087 --> 01:00:34.088
Oh, my gosh!

01:02:00.842 --> 01:02:03.177
Please stop. I beg you.

01:02:25.450 --> 01:02:27.326
- Grab him.
- Come here, you bastard!

01:02:53.436 --> 01:02:55.396
I'll help you get to heaven.

01:04:11.639 --> 01:04:15.726
DEAR X

01:06:36.200 --> 01:06:38.202
Subtitles by Ho-young Yun